CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 13, 1955, pg. 9 reads: " 'Operations...Gettysburg' - A number of members of the Youth Department of the Centre Avenue YMCA left Tuesday on a one-day trip to Gettysburg. Crowded into the one-day schedule was a guided sight-seeing tour of the memorial battlefield, and the chance to see many scenic spots between Pittsburgh and Gettysburg. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of the Youth Department of the Centre Avenue YMCA and chaperones, standing in front of Greyhound bus with Operations Gettysburg sign, before trip to Gettysburg
